Georeferenced maps in the State Library of Victoria's collections

This dashboard provides information on digitised maps from the State Library of Victoria's collection that have been georeferenced using Allmaps. It is updated every two hours. Check Allmaps Latest for more recent additions.

See the project documentation for information on how you can be involved!
